data.description: Great home in beautiful Saraland! You must see this 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home. Outside, the fenced back yard features a patio area, and several mature satsuma trees. The property is located in a quiet neighborhood with minimal traffic, this area provides convenience to the interstate and all the Saraland/Satsuma area has to offer. A great home for a first time home buyer or investor. This wonderful home will not be available for long. Schedule a showing today! The listing broker makes no representation of square footage accuracy. Buyer to verify.
